      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is put for the greatest part of it by a synecdoche, very frequent in Scripture and all authors; and so the Gadites might possess a part of it. And thus both Bashan and Gilead are used for parts of them, ",
        "children": []
      },
