        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". And as it is unquestionably true that Gilead is taken sometimes more largely for all the land of the Israelites beyond Jordan, sometimes more strictly for that part of it which borders upon Mount Gilead; of which ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
